lock","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"f85354c5-3d75-4541-9c24-0353e222f6b6","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I learn from thy last letter of Giovan Simoni\u0027s death. No greater grief could have befallen me, for although I am old I still hoped that I should see him before he died and before I died. God has\u00A0willed it otherwise. Patience! I should like to hear more of how he died, and if he died shriven and\u00A0having received the Sacrament, observing all the ordinances of the Church: for if I know that he received them I shall grieve the less.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"2cc50e2b-83e0-4651-aa2a-51a355247c50","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1d896705-6ab5-417f-be47-b2fc6c4d9401","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"84c5a1dd-e118-4cbd-b86e-e5f3ef448c7e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":12,"end":12,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"a887a272-de63-4f9d-b30b-246459988eaa","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":25,"end":27,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"fc4a1b01-a056-49af-87c2-f42b8937c1ec","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":44,"end":56,"value":"d8b71a68-0171-4aa5-a446-69fbdbd88655","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0915338f-1a91-49d2-9050-0498f7d7f688","type":"attitude/grief","start":67,"end":198,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b47b7003-10a1-4e9f-9926-d32e0d27c327","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":104,"end":105,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"41731b1e-b527-48e4-b6ad-185fb2d69b11","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":121,"end":121,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"52e7c619-a481-4